                                "stop": 10.74,
                                "byte_start": 90894,
                                "byte_stop": 133944,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 90-1918, Kraft General Foods versus Iowa Department of Revenue and Finance will be announced by Justice Stevens."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 10.74,
                        "stop": 79.02,
